pageProduct.name: Wagner Olive Leaf 3600+ 100 Capsules
pageProduct.description:
General Information

Contains Zinc, which is important for the health and function of the immune system
Provides antioxidant support
Helps to maintain general wellbeing

Features
Olive Leaf contains the constituent oleuropein an antioxidant that helps to scavenge free radicals.
Zinc is an essential trace mineral which plays a role in the visual, reproductive and immune systems.
This formula blends Olive Leaf extract and Zinc in a convenient capsule.

Warnings

Always read the label; take only as directed.
WARNING: May be dangerous if taken in large amounts or for a long period.

Formulated without:
Gluten, wheat, dairy products, egg, soy, corn, artificial colours, artificial flavours, artificial sweeteners or preservatives.

Ingredients

Each capsule provides
Standardised herbal extract equiv. dry
Olea europaea (Olive) leaf    3.6g
Equiv. Oleuropein     80mg
Zinc (as Zinc oxide)     15mg

Directions

Take 2 capsules daily with food, or as directed by your healthcare professional.
